<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Masterclass: Encapsulation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/terminal.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/spherification.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="terminal-container">
        <header>
            <h1><a href="/dashboard" style="color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.5rem;">&lt; Back</a> | Encapsulation</h1>
            <p>Turn liquid modifiers into bursting, edible caviar.</p>
        </header>

        <main style="max-width: 950px; margin: 0 auto;">
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
                
                <div class="module-card" style="padding: 2.5rem;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Select Modifier</h3>
                    
                    <select id="caviarSelect" class="elegant-input" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                        <option value="olive">Olive Brine (Savory/Salty)</option>
                        <option value="cassis">Creme de Cassis (Sweet/Berry)</option>
                        <option value="aperol">Aperol (Bitter/Citrus)</option>
                    </select>

                    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        By dissolving Sodium Alginate into your chosen modifier and dropping it into a Calcium bath, the ions instantly polymerize to create a delicate, gelatinous skin around the liquid.
                    </p>

                    <button id="dropBtn" style="width: 100%; padding: 15px; font-size: 1rem;">
                        Dispense Droplet
                    </button>
                    <button id="clearBtn" style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; background: transparent; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        Clear Bath
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="lab-station">
                    <div class="pipette"></div>
                    <div class="calcium-bath">
                        <div class="bath-liquid" id="bathZone"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="module-card" id="recipeCard" style="padding: 3rem; background: rgba(30, 45, 70, 0.3); border-color: var(--accent-blue);">
                <h2 id="recipeTitle" style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-align: center; color: var(--text-main);">
                    </h2>
                <p id="recipeDesc" style="text-align: center; color: var(--accent-blue); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    </p>
                
                <hr style="border: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(138, 180, 248, 0.2); margin-bottom: 2rem;">

                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem;">
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Caviar Prep</h3>
                        <ul id="recipePrep" style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 1.2rem;">
                            </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Build</h3>
                        <ul id="recipeBuild" style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 1.2rem;">
                             </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/sphere-engine.js"></script>
</body>
</html>